%26quot%3BI%20still%20see%20the%20bilateral%20relations%20between%20the%20air%20forces%20as%20very%20superficial%20and%20symbolic%2C%26quot%3B%20Aboudouh%20said.%20%26quot%3BStrategic%20depth%20in%20military%20partnerships%20takes%20time%20to%20build.%20I%20don't%20see%20this%20relationship%20developing%20into%20something%20similar%20to%20what%20the%20UAE%20Air%20Force%20has%20with%20France%20or%20even%20Russia%20anytime%20soon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERoblin%20pointed%20out%20that%20while%20the%20L-15s%20are%20%26quot%3Brespectable%20advanced%20trainers%20sold%20at%20a%20bargain%20unit%20price%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20lack%20the%20benefit%20of%20%26quot%3Bcommon%20systems%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20F-16%20and%20Rafale%20jets%2C%20which%20Emirati%20fighter%20pilots%20will%20eventually%20graduate%20to%20fly.%20Furthermore%2C%20the%20Emirati%20air%20force%20fighter%20fleet%20is%20already%20large%20for%20such%20a%20small%20country%2C%20making%20it%20unlikely%20the%20L-15s%20will%20serve%20any%20combat%20role.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BSo%20the%20sale%2C%20like%20the%20common%20exercises%2C%20serves%20as%20a%20warning%20signal%20to%20the%20US%20that%20the%20UAE%20may%20take%20its%20money%20elsewhere%2C%26quot%3B%20Roblin%20said.%20%26quot%3BOf%20course%2C%20there's%20a%20risk%20of%20that%20backfiring%20and%20convincing%20Washington%20it%20can't%20be%20trusted%20with%20more%20advanced%20US%20hardware%20like%20the%20F-35%20if%20ties%20with%20China%20grow%20too%20cozy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAboudouh%20believes%20it's%20%26quot%3Bhard%20to%20predict%26quot%3B%20if%20the%20UAE%20might%20eventually%20acquire%20fifth-generation%20Chinese%20aircraft.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20main%20factor%20at%20play%20here%20is%20the%20US%20vision%20for%20its%20military%20relations%20with%20the%20UAE%2C%26quot%3B%20Aboudouh%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20other%20words%2C%20at%20a%20time%20of%20extensi