.%20The%20Emirates%20is%20already%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fpauliddon%2F2023%2F09%2F15%2Fuae-reportedly-seeking-role-in-south-koreas-kf-21-fighter-jet-program%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereportedly%20interested%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20investing%20in%20the%20KF-21.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20UAE%20would%20probably%20not%20be%20interested%20in%20procuring%20advanced%20fourth-generation%20Chinese%20fighters%20either%2C%20especially%20given%20the%20enormous%20Rafale%20order%20it%20just%20signed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERoblin%20also%20questioned%20why%20the%20UAE%20would%20buy%20jets%20like%20the%20J-10%20and%20J-16%20from%20China%20when%20it%20already%20has%20access%20to%20equivalent%20or%20superior%20Western%20jets%20like%20the%20F-15EX%2C%20F-16V%2C%20and%2C%20of%20course%2C%20the%20Rafale.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIntroducing%20such%20Chinese%20aircraft%20dependent%20on%20different%20weapons%20and%20communication%20ecosystems%20would%20be%20logistically%20senseless%20unless%20there%20was%20a%20broader%20project%20to%20convert%20to%20a%20Chinese%20fleet%2C%26quot%3B%20Robin%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BBut%20I'm%20skeptical%20the%20UAE%20would%20go%20all-in%20in%20that%20direction.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuae-forges-china-ties-but-wont-get-j20-stealth-fighter-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715202001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663bcd7fb4abc992e8c70bf5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuae-forges-china-ties-but-wont-get-j20-stealth-fighter-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20is%20building%20ties%20to%20China's%20air%20force%20in%20what%20m