just%20%24100.%20Now%20he%20stands%20to%20win%20%241.7%20million%2C%20representing%20a%20potential%20return%20of%201%2C690%2C900%25%20if%20the%20bet%20pans%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20ticket%20to%20pay%20out%20the%20%241.7%20million%2C%20the%20Texas%20Rangers%20had%20to%20win%20the%20MLB%20World%20Series%20(check)%2C%20the%20Kansas%20City%20Chiefs%20had%20to%20win%20the%20NFL%20Super%20Bowl%20(also%20check).%20The%20final%20piece%20is%20an%20NBA%20title%20for%20the%20Thunder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20never%20bet%20that%20high%20on%20a%20future%2C%20especially%20a%20lottery%20ticket%20like%20this%20one.%20They%20gave%20me%20a%20high%20max%20and%20I%20just%20said%2C%20'You%20know%20what%3F%20This%20one%20time%2C%20max%20it%20out%2C%20let's%20go.'%20%5BI%5D%20never%20do%20that.%20%5BAnd%5D%20here%20we%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Dcfeb765f9c016bcc4a357c1b8a6f5c3767ede3adf313ea771ddeaffbb487d9a8%26postID%3D663bc1632c3267408d0cbef8%26postSlug%3Dmillion-dollar-okc-thunder-parlay-bet-nba-secondary-market-hedge-2024-5%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.espn.com%252Fespn%252Fbetting%252Fstory%252F_%252Fid%252F40102166%252Fmillion-dollar-parlay-ticket-bettor-oklahoma-city-thunder-texas-rangers-kansas-city-chiefs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShelton%20told%20ESPN%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20it's%20a%20parlay%20bet%2C%20it's%20an%20all-or-nothing%20payout%20scheme%2C%20meaning%20Shelton%20gets%20absolutely%20nothing%20besides%20a%20thrilling%20experience%20if%20the%20Thunder%20lose%20one%20of%20their%20next%20three%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20unless%20he%20cashes%20out%20on%20the%20ticket%20early%20with%20DraftKings%2C%20the%20sportsbook%20through%20which%20he%20placed%20the%20original%20bet.%20Other%20options%20include%20betting%20on%20other%20NBA%20Finals%20outcomes%20%E2%80%94%20or%20even%20against%20the%20Thunder's%20current%20opponent%20%E2%80%94%20as%20a%20hedge%20against%20Oklahoma%20City%20falling%20short.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShelton%20investigated%20how%20much%20DraftKings%20would%20pay%20him%20to%20cash%20out%20his%20%241.7%20million%20parlay%20ticket%20after%20the%20Thunder%20won%20their%20first%20series%20against%20the%20New%20Orleans%20Pelicans%2C%20but%20at%20about%20%2475%2C000%2C%20Shelton%20thought%20that%20was%20a%20bad%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20he%20sought%20out%20the%20novel%20solution%20of%20offering%20other%20sports%20bettors%20a%20chance%20to%20get%20in%20on%20the%20bet%20on%20the%20secondary%20market.%20Using%20a%20service%20called%20WagerWire%2C%20Shelton%20opened%20his%20ticket%20up%20to%20potential%20offers%20from%20outside%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShelton%20has%20so%20far%20received%20offers%20from%20outside%20investors%20for%20as%20much%20as%20%24200%2C000%2C%20but%20part%20of%20the%20challenge%20is%20verifying%20those%20offers%20are%20legitimate.%20His%20top%20priority%20is%20to%20protect%20his%20ticket%2C%20ESPN%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20an%20entire%20separate%20industry%20dedicated%20to%20playing%20matchmaking%20between%20high-rolling%20sports%20bettors%20and%20opportunities%20with%20high%20initial%20buy-ins%2C%20like%20Shelton's%20parlay%20ticket.%20ESPN%20noted%20that%20there%20is%20a%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bconcierge%20service%26quot%3B%20called%20White%20Glove%20Bets%20that%20boasts%20a%20roster%20of%C2%A0%20%26quot%3Bhigh-level%20VIPs%26quot%3B%20whose%20risk%20tolerance%20is%20often%20too%20high%20for%20major%20sportsbooks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShelton%20is%20still%20retaining%20full%20ownership%20of%20his%20ticket%20until%20he%20finds%20a%20suitable%20offer%2C%20but%20his%20experience%20seeking%20investors%20on%20WagerWire%20offers%20an%20early%20look%20at%20the%20markets%20will%20continue%20to%20crop%20up%20following%20the%20legalization%20of%20sports%20betting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20Shelton%20will%20be%20closely%20watching%20the%20Thunder.%20They%20currently%20have%20a%201-0%20lead%20in%20their%20best-of-seven%20Western%20Conference%20semifinal%20series%20against%20the%20Dallas%20Mavericks%2C%20leaving%20Shelton%20a%20mere%2011%20victories%20from%20gambling%20immortality%2C%20regardless%20of%20what%20he%20ends%20up%20doing%20with%20his%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillion-dollar-okc-thunder-parlay-bet-nba-secondary-market-hedge-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715198238000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663bd4daf27898f532d533fe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillion-dollar-okc-thunder-parlay-bet-nba-secondary-market-hedge-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22His%20parlay%20ticket%20included%20championships%20for%20the%20Texas%20Rangers%2C%20Kansas%20City%20Chiefs%2C%20and%20Oklahoma%20City%20Thunder.%20He's%20two-thirds%20of%20the%20way%20there.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mfox%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Fox)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillion-dollar-okc-thunder-parlay-bet-nba-secondary-market-hedge-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22An%20escalating%20cold%20war%20between%20US%20and%20China%20would%20be%20a%20blow%20to%20global%20growth%2C%20IMF%20official%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20and%20Chinese%20flags%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663bc793b4abc992e8c707f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPedro%20Pardo%2FAFP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20brewing%20US-China%20cold%20war%20could%20drag%20global%20economic%20growth%20down%20as%20much%20as%207%25%2C%20an%20IMF%20official%20said%20this%20week.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20emergence%20of%20%26quot%3Bconnector%26quot%3B%20countries%20is%20why%20the%20effect%20of%20ongoing%20tensions%20hasn't%20been%20bigger.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETrade%20fragmentation%20carries%20a%20higher%20price%20tag%20compared%20to%20the%20US-Soviet%20cold%20war%2C%20the%20official%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20more%20intense%20cold%20war%20between%20the%20US%20and%20China%20would%20have%20a%20potentially%20dire%20impact%20on%20the%20global%20economy%2C%20according%20to%20an%20official%20from%20the%20International%20Monetary%20Fund.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.imf.org%2Fen%2FNews%2FArticles%2F2024%2F05%2F07%2Fsp-geopolitics-impact-global-trade-and-dollar-gita-gopinath%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESpeaking%20at%20Stanford%20University%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20IMF%20deputy%20managing%20director%20Gita%20Gopinath%20said%20that%20while%20US-China%20tensions%20haven't%20yet%20devolved%20into%20a%20full-blown%20cold%20war%2C%20such%20an%20escalation%20would%20be%20a%20major%20headwind%20to%20global%20growth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20IMF%20predicts%20that%20the%20global%20economy%20could%20incur%20economic%20costs%20equivalent%20to%20as%20much%20as%207%25%20of%20the%20world's%20GDP%20in%20the%20worst-case%20scenario%20and%20take%20a%200.2%25%20hit%20to%20growth%20in%20milder%20scenarios.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20fund%2C%20lower-income%20countries%20could%20suffer%20four%20times%20the%20loss%20of%20economic%20output%20compared%20to%20other%20nations%20if%20commodity%20markets%20split%20into%20blocs%20aligned%20with%20either%20China%20or%20the%20US.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConflict%20between%20the%20world's%20two%20largest%20economies%20has%20escalated%20to%20a%20new%20heights%20since%20the%20pandemic.%20With%20China's%20growing%20economic%20ambitions%20and%20recent%20aggressions%20against%20neighboring%20countries%2C%20the%20US%20has%20put%20up%20new%20guardrails%20in%20its%20dealing%20with%20China%2C%20including%20restricting%20trade%20in%20key%20areas%20both%20countries%20are%20racing%20to%20dominate%2C%20such%20as%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIMF%20data%20shows%20that%20more%20than%203%2C000%20trade%20restrictions%20were%20imposed%20globally%20in%202022%20and%202023%2C%20more%20than%20triple%20the%20count%20from%202019%2C%20with%20Gopinath%20saying%20that%20trade%20within%20the%20China%20and%20US%20blocs%20has%20dropped%20compared%20to%20intra-group%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tensions%20have%20also%20dented%20flows%20of%20foreign%20capital%20to%20China%2C%20with%20the%20country%20suffering%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-foreign-investment-deficit-beijing-xi-jinping-zero-covid-2023-11%5C%22%3Efirst%20foreign%20investment%20deficit%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20November%202023%20and%20seeing%20further%20declines%20in%20the%20first%20three%20months%20of%202024.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20emergence%20of%20%26quot%3Bconnector%26quot%3B%20countries%2C%20which%20have%20acted%20as%20neutral%20go-betweens%20for%20the%20US%20and%20China%2C%20may%20be%20the%20reason%20the%20impact%20of%20tensions%20hasn't%20been%20greater.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20emergence%20of%20these%20'connector'%20countries%E2%80%94perhaps%20most%20notably%20Mexico%20and%20Vietnam%E2%80%94may%20have%20helped%20cushion%20the%20global%20economic%20impact%20of%20direct%20trade%20decoupling%20between%20the%20U.S.%20and%20China%2C%26quot%3B%20Gopinath%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZooming%20out%2C%20Gopinath%20highlighted%20that%20geopolitical%20instability%20in%20regions%20like%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20turmoil%20stemming%20from%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%20has%20sparked%20trade%20turbulence%20unseen%20since%20the%20Cold%20War.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20IMF%20emphasized%20that%20trade%20fragmentation%20carries%20a%20higher%20price%20tag%20today%2C%20w