20and%20for%20reducing%20supply%20chain%20risks%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20industrialists%20Gautam%20Adani%20and%20Mukesh%20Ambani%20playing%20a%20fundamental%20role%20in%20shaping%20the%20economic%20superpower%20the%20country%20will%20become%20in%20the%20coming%20decades%2C%20according%20to%20a%20CNN%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20says%20to%20spur%20growth%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20begun%20a%20massive%20infrastructure%20transformation%20by%20spending%20billions%20on%20building%20roads%2C%20ports%2C%20airports%20and%20railways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20heavily%20promoting%20digital%20connectivity%2C%20which%20can%20improve%20both%20commerce%20and%20daily%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20Mr%20Adani%20and%20Mr%20Ambani%20have%20become%20key%20allies%20as%20the%20country%20embarks%20on%20this%20revolution%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorth%20%243.7%20trillion%20in%202023%2C%20India%20is%20the%20world's%20fifth%20largest%20economy%2C%20jumping%20four%20spots%20in%20the%20rankings%20during%20PM%20Modi's%20decade%20in%20office%20and%20leapfrogging%20the%20United%20Kingdom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20comfortably%20placed%20to%20expand%20at%20an%20annual%20rate%20of%20at%20least%206%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20coming%20few%20years%2C%20but%20analysts%20say%20the%20country%20should%20be%20targeting%20growth%20of%20eight%20per%20cent%20or%20more%20if%20it%20wants%20to%20become%20an%20economic%20superpower.%20Sustained%20expansion%20will%20push%20India%20higher%20up%20the%20ranks%20of%20the%20world's%20biggest%20economies%2C%20with%20some%20observers%20forecasting%20the%20South%20Asian%20nation%20to%20become%20number%20three%20behind%20only%20the%20US%20and%20China%20by%202027%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CNN%20analysis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20and%20Reliance%20Industries%20-%20the%20two%20sprawling%20conglomerates%20having%20valuations%20worth%20over%20%24200%20billion%20each%20-%20have%20established%20businesses%20in%20sectors%20ranging%20from%20fossil%20fuels%20and%20clean%20energy%20to%20media%20and%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInvestors%20have%20been%20cheering%20the%20duo's%20ability%20to%20adroitly%20bet%20on%20sectors%20prioritised%20for%20development%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20currently%20campaigning%20for%20his%20third%20consecutive%20term%20to%20lead%20India.%20The%20South%20Asian%20country%20is%20poised%20to%20become%20a%2021st-century%20economic%20powerhouse%2C%20offering%20a%20real%20alternative%20to%20China%20for%20investors%20hunting%20for%20growth%20and%20manufacturers%20looking%20to%20reduce%20risks%20in%20their%20supply%20chains%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20result%2C%20these%20three%20men%20--%20PM%20Modi%2C%20Mr%20Ambani%20and%20Mr%20Adani%20--%20are%20playing%20a%20fundamental%20role%20in%20shaping%20the%20economic%20superpower%20India%20will%20become%20in%20the%20coming%20decades%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20kind%20of%20power%20and%20influence%20being%20enjoyed%20by%20the%20two%20Indian%20tycoons%20has%20been%20seen%20before%20in%20other%20countries%20%26quot%3Bexperiencing%20periods%20of%20rapid%20industrialisation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20both%20Mr%20Adani%20and%20Mr%20Ambani%20are%20often%20compared%20by%20journalists%20to%20John%20D%20Rockefeller%2C%20who%20became%20America's%20first%20billionaire%20during%20the%20Gilded%20Age%2C%20a%2030-year%20period%20in%20the%20last%20decades%20of%20the%2019th%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20something%20that%20America%20and%20lots%20of%20other%20countries%20have%20already%20gone%20through.%20Britain%20in%20the%201820s%2C%20South%20Korea%20in%20the%201960s%20and%2070s%2C%20and%20you%20could%20argue%20China%20in%20the%202000s%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20James%20Crabtree%2C%20the%20author%20of%20The%20Billionaire%20Raj%2C%20a%20book%20about%20India's%20wealthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMumbai%2C%20which%20is%20considered%20India's%20financial%20capital%2C%20has%20the%20imprint%20of%20the%20two%20tycoons%20everywhere%2C%20from%20high-rise%20apartment%20buildings%20branded%20with%20Adani%20Realty%20to%20cultural%20institutions%20named%20after%20the%20Ambani%20clan%2C%20and%20even%20the%20international%20airport%2C%20which%20is%20operated%20by%20Adani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20spaces%20need%20no%20names%20or%20bright%20labels%2C%20but%20their%20affiliations%20are%20just%20as%20obvious.%20Everyone%20in%20Mumbai%20knows%20who%20lives%20in%20Antilia%20--%20the%20personal%20skyscraper%20of%20Ambani%20and%20his%20family%2C%20which%20reportedly%20cost%20%242%20billion%20to%20build%20and%20boasts%20a%20spa%2C%20three%20helipads%20and%20a%2050-seat%20theatre.%20The%2027-story%20building%20sits%20on%20a%20street%20dubbed%20'Billionaires'%20Row%2C'%20its%20jutting%20geometric%20architecture%20looming%20over%20the%20neighbourhood.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CNN%20report%20also%20mentions%20the%20grand%20pre-wedding%20celebration%20of%20Mukesh%20Ambani's%20son%20Anant%20Ambani%20in%20March%20this%20year%2C%20when%20billionaires%20and%20movie%20stars%20from%20around%20the%20world%20jetted%20to%20Jamnagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%2C%20Bill%20Gates%20and%20Ivanka%20Trump%20were%20among%20the%20many%20high-profile%20celebrities%20in%20attendance.%20The%20three-day%20celebration%2C%20which%20saw%20performances%20by%20popstar%20Rihanna%20and%20magician%20David%20Blaine%2C%20transfixed%20India%20and%20further%20underscored%20Mr%20Ambani's%20growing%20global%20clout.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuido%20Cozzi%2C%20professor%20of%20macroeconomics%20at%20the%20University%20of%20St%20Gallen%20in%20Switzerland%2C%20said%20these%20%26quot%3Bconglomerates%20are%20very%2C%20very%20important%20and%20very%20well%20connected%2C%26quot%3B%20noting%20that%20both%20the%20Adani%20Group%20and%20Reliance%20Industries%20were%20founded%20years%20before%20PM%20Modi%20came%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20not%20typical%20stagnant%20monopolistic%20conglomerates.%20They%20are%20pretty%20dynamic%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Cozzi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20are%20they%20playing%20%26quot%3Ban%20important%20role%26quot%3B%20in%20building%20infrastructure%2C%20which%20helps%20%26quot%3Bgrowth%20directly%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20the%20two%20business%20groups%20are%20also%20helping%20the%20country%20expand%20%26quot%3Bindirectly%26quot%3B%20by%20boosting%20connectivity%20through%20digital%20innovation%2C%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReliance%20was%20founded%20by%20Mr%20Ambani's%20father%2C%20Dhirubhai%2C%20as%20a%20small%20yarn%20trading%20firm%20in%20Mumbai%20in%201957.%20Over%20the%20next%20few%20decades%2C%20it%20grew%20into%20a%20colossal%20conglomerate%20spanning%20energy%2C%20petrochemicals%20and%20telecommunications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMukesh%20Ambani%20has%20not%20only%20upended%20India's%20telecom%20sector%20in%20less%20than%20a%20decade%20but%20also%20become%20a%20top%20player%20in%20sectors%20ranging%20from%20media%20to%20retail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20says%20that%20Mukesh%20Ambani's%20ambition%20and%20breathless%20pace%20of%20expansion%20is%20matched%20by%20Mr%20Adani%2C%20%26quot%3B...who%20now%20helms%20businesses%20ranging%20from%20ports%20and%20power%20to%20defence%20and%20aerospace%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20first-generation%20entrepreneur%2C%20the%2062-year-old%20began%20his%20career%20with%20diamond%20trading%2C%20before%20setting%20up%20a%20commodity%20trading%20business%20in%201988%2C%20which%20later%20evolved%20into%20Adani%20Enterprises%20Limited%20(AEL).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20January%20note%20by%20American%20brokerage%20firm%20Cantor%20Fitzgerald%2C%20AEL%20%26quot%3Bis%20at%20the%20core%20of%20everything%20India%20wants%20to%20accomplish.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20functions%20as%20an%20incubator%20for%20Mr%20Adani's%20businesses.%20Many%20have%20been%20spun%20out%20and%20become%20leading%20players%20in%20their%20respective%20sectors.%20According%20to%20Cantor%2C%20the%20firm's%20current%20focus%20on%20airports%2C%20roads%20and%20energy%20make%20it%20%26quot%3Ba%20unique%20long-term%20investment%20opportunity%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20notes%20that%20while%20both%20the%20barons%20built%20much%20of%20their%20fortune%20from%20fossil%20fuels%2C%20they%20are%20now%20investing%20billions%20in%20clean%20energy.%20Notably%2C%20their%20green%20energy%20pivot%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20India%20has%20set%20itself%20some%20ambitious%20climate%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20notes%20that%20despite%20India's%20success%20in%20terms%20of%20growth%20rate%2C%20soaring%20youth%20unemployment%20and%20inequality%20remain%20stubbornly%20persistent%20problems.%20In%202022%2C%20the%20country%20ranked%20a%20lowly%20147%20on%20gross%20domestic%20product%20(GDP)%20per%20person%2C%20a%20measure%20of%20living%20standards%2C%20according%20to%20the%20World%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20parties%20in%20India%20have%20targeted%20the%20BJP-led%20government%20alleging%20it%20has%20ties%20with%20the%20country's%20super-rich%20and%20over%20the%20meteoric%20rise%20of%20Mr%20Adani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%20PM%20Modi's%20%26quot%3Bperceived%20relationship%20with%20the%20billionaires%26quot%3B%20is%20once%20again%20being%20questioned%20by%20rivals%20during%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20processes%2C%20particularly%20more%20transparency%20in%20the%20allocation%20of%20India's%20natural%20resources%20and%20the%20overhauling%20of%20the%20country's%20bankruptcy%20laws%2C%20have%20seen%20important%20reforms%20under%20PM%20Modi%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20report%2C%20some%20experts%20say%20that%20%26quot%3Bsome%20amount%20of%20closeness%26quot%3B%20between%20politicians%20and%20business%20elite%20%26quot%3Bcan%20help%20in%20growing%20the%20nation%20faster.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20suggests%20that%20India%20needs%20to%20encourage%20entrepreneurship%20and%20innovation%20bringing%20more%20firms%20into%20the%20sphere%2C%20as%20a%20country%2C%20where%20millions%20of%20people%20join%20the%20labour%20force%20every%20month%2C%20can't%20be%20absorbed%20by%20a%20few%20conglomerates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20phenomenal%20...%20entrepreneurs%2C%20who%20have%20been%20able%20to%20sustain%20steady%20growth%20and%20development%20in%20a%20vibrant%20yet%20sometimes%20chaotic%20political%20and%20business%20environment%20that%20exists%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rohit%20Lamba%2C%20an%20economist%20at%20Pennsylvania%20State%20University%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20co-author%20of%20Breaking%20the%20Mould%2C%20a%202023%20book%20that%20examines%20how%20Indian%20economy%20can%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20cannot%20grow%20rich%20before%20it%20becomes%20old%20on%20the%20back%20of%20a%20few%20big%20firms%20like%20Adani%20or%20Ambani...India%20should%20make%20more%20firms%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20says%20India%20has%20other%20conglomerates%20as%20well.%20The%20156-year-old%20Tata%20Group%20wields%20immense%20power%20over%20various%20key%20sectors%20ranging%20from%20steel%20to%20aviation%2C%20but%20it%20often%20does%20not%20invite%20the%20same%20scrutiny%20as%20the%20newer%20conglomerates%2C%20mainly%20because%20it%20is%20controlled%20by%20philanthropic%20trusts%20and%20not%20run%20as%20a%20family%20dynasty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20been%20the%20fastest-growing%20large%20economy%20in%20the%20last%20three%20financial%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Medi