20mode%20to%20introduce%20them%20to%20these%20powerhouses%20of%20nutrition%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shashidhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20millets%20are%20procured%20from%20their%20own%20farms%2C%20and%20other%20farmers%20in%20Theni%2C%20Dharmapuri%2C%20and%20Krishnagiri%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20venture%20is%20entirely%20self-funded%2C%20with%20each%20of%20the%20four%20founders%20investing%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20their%20savings%20into%20realising%20their%20dream.%20Their%20most%20significant%20hurdle%20post-launch%20has%20been%20the%20widespread%20lack%20of%20awareness%20surrounding%20millets.%20To%20address%20this%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20been%20diligently%20engaged%20in%20consumer%20education%20initiatives%2C%20conducting%20awareness%20campaigns%20in%20schools%2C%20colleges%2C%20and%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20realised%20that%20the%20first%20step%20was%20to%20create%20customer%20awareness.%20We%20started%20visiting%20schools%20and%20colleges%20to%20educate%20the%20youth%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20nutritious%20eating%20habits.%20We%20believe%20that%20knowledge%20is%20the%20key%20to%20transformation%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Shashidhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20take%20students%20on%20a%20factory%20tour%20to%20show%20them%20the%20manufacturing%20process.%20In%202023%2C%20they%20established%20a%20factory%20in%20Trichy%2C%20with%20a%2010%2C000-litre%20capacity%20per%20shift.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20opened%20outlets%20in%20Hyderabad%20near%20the%20Statue%20of%20Equality%20and%20one%20in%20Rajahmundry.%20They%20are%20poised%20to%20launch%2010%20to%2012%20more%20outlets%20in%20the%20coming%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20us%2C%20community%20engagement%20is%20equally%20important.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20movement%20to%20bring%20back%20the%20treasures%20of%20our%20ancestors%2C%20adapted%20to%20meet%20the%20needs%20of%20today%E2%80%99s%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Prabu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20country%20is%20seeing%20an%20increasing%20shift%20towards%20millets%2C%20this%20is%20a%20novel%20way%20to%20include%20them%20in%20our%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Prabu%20Venugopal%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715180752000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsiri-ice-cream-1715178095.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D349369%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prabu%20Venugopal%2C%20Shashidhar%2C%20Arun%20Prakash%2C%20and%20Bhargav%20left%20their%20comfortable%20careers%20to%20introduce%20a%20healthy%2C%20vegan%20ice%20cream%20alternative%20made%20using%20millets.%20They%20founded%20Siri%20Millet%20Ice%20Creams%20in%20Trichy%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20are%20actively%20healthy%20eating%20habits%20through%20educational%20initiatives.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F349369%2Fsiri-millet-vegan-ice-cream-trichy-non-dairy-healthy-frozen-dessert%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Air%20India%20Express%20To%20Curtail%20Flights%20Over%20Next%20Few%20Days%20Amid%20Crew%20Crisis%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20no%20resolution%20in%20sight%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bmass%20leave%26quot%3B%20crisis%20being%20faced%20by%20the%20airline%2C%20Air%20India%20Express%20CEO%20Aloke%20Singh%20has%20written%20to%20employees%20and%20said%20that%20the%20number%20of%20flights%20being%20operated%20will%20be%20reduced%20over%20the%20next%20few%20days.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20Tuesday%20night%2C%20the%20airline%20has%20had%20to%20cancel%20over%2090%20flights%20after%20300%20senior%20cabin%20crew%20members%20reported%20sick%20at%20the%20last%20minute%20and%20then%20switched%20off%20their%20cellphones.%20Hundreds%20of%20passengers%20were%20left%20stranded.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Air%20India%20Express%20Employees%20Union%20also%20wrote%20to%20the%20management%20and%20%26quot%3Bhighlighted%20a%20stark%20departure%20from%20commitments%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20letter%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20said%20over%20100%20cabin%20crew%20members%20had%20reported%20sick%2C%20severely%20disrupting%20operations%2C%20and%20that%20the%20impact%20was%20%26quot%3Bdisproportionate%26quot%3B%20because%20the%20action%20was%20taken%20by%20senior%20employees.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20disruptions%20have%20cascaded%20across%20the%20network%2C%20forcing%20us%20to%20curtail%20the%20schedules%20over%20the%20next%20few%20days.%20We%20had%20to%20do%20this%20to%20cope%20with%20the%20non-availability%20of%20crew%20and%20to%20recover%20schedules.%20This%20act%20is%20certainly%20not%20representative%20of%20the%202%2C000-odd%20cabin%20crew%20colleagues%20in%20the%20company%20who%20continue%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20call%20of%20duty%20and%20serve%20our%20guests%20with%20dedication%20and%20pride.%20I%20am%20thankful%20to%20all%20who%20are%20standing%20by%20the%20airline%20in%20this%20hour%20of%20crisis%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CEO%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpressing%20his%20gratitude%20to%20employees%20from%20other%20departments%20that%20have%20pitched%20in%20to%20assist%20in%20the%20operations%20sphere%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20said%20the%20management%20is%20available%20to%20address%20concerns%20at%20both%20group%20and%20individual%20levels.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20on%20a%20journey%20towards%20growth%20and%20transformation%2C%20which%20will%20make%20us%20one%20the%20largest%20airlines%20in%20the%20region.%20Enough%20professional%20growth%20opportunities%20are%20there%20for%20all...%20Hope%20to%20see%20things%20get%20resolved%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Well-Being%20Should%20Be%20Priority'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh's%20letter%20was%20followed%20by%20a%20post%20on%20an%20internal%20forum%20by%20a%20senior%20crew%20member%20of%20Air%20India%20Express%2C%20who%20said%20that%20the%20well-being%20of%20employees%20should%20be%20the%20priority.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20appreciate%20your%20(Mr%20Singh's)%20message%2C%20and%20I%20want%20to%20express%20my%20concerns%20respectfully.%20In%20times%20when%20our%20colleagues%20are%20unwell%2C%20it's%20crucial%20to%20prioritise%20their%20well-being.%20Understanding%20their%20health%20conditions%20should%20be%20our%20foremost%20concern%20rather%20than%20any%20other%20agenda%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20crew%20member%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20disheartening%20to%20learn%20about%20the%20number%20of%20employees%20falling%20ill%20simultaneously%2C%20which%20has%20indeed%20disrupted%20our%20operations.%20However%2C%20attributing%20this%20solely%20to%20incompetence%20overlooks%20the%20dedication%20and%20honesty%20with%20which%20our%20crew%20have%20served%20our%20guests%20until%20now.%20You%20mentioned%20departmental%20town%20hall%20meetings%2C%20but%20it%20feels%20more%20like%20a%20one-way%20communication%20channel.%20I%20urge%20you%20to%20genuinely%20listen%20to%20our%20colleagues'%20concerns%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20post%20read.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20part%20of%20the%20CEO's%20letter%20which%20spoke%20about%20growth%20and%20transformation%2C%20the%20crew%20member%20said%20that%20while%20that%20thought%20is%20commendable%2C%20%26quot%3Bensuring%20our%20team's%20alignment%20and%20support%26quot%3B%20should%20come%20first.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20section%20of%20employees%20are%20unhappy%20with%20a%20new%20merit-based%20assessment%20system.%20The%20Air%20India%20Express%20Employees%20Union%20(AIXEU)%20has%20also%20accused%20the%20airline%20of%20mismanagement%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20equality%20in%20staff%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20to%20Natarajan%20Chandrasekaran%2C%20the%20Chairman%20of%20Tata%