rofile%5C%22%3EMakoto%20Taniyama%3C%2Fa%3E%20(2%2F0)%20bagged%20two%20each%20in%20the%20match%20held%20at%20the%20Sano%20International%20Cricket%20Ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETur%20Sumaya%20(4%20off%2011)%20was%20the%20top-scorer%20for%20Mongolia%2C%20while%20opener%20Namsrai%20Bat-yalalt%20faced%20a%20maximum%2012%20deliveries.%20This%20was%20the%20second%20T20I%20of%20a%20seven-match%20series%2C%20while%20the%20third%20one%2C%20slated%20later%20in%20the%20day%2C%20did%20not%20yield%20any%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20T20I%2C%20Mongolia%20were%20bowled%20out%20for%2033%20in%20reply%20to%20Japan's%20199%20for%205%2C%20enduring%20a%20166-run%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20Mongolia's%20fifth%20T20I%20appearance%2C%20having%20made%20international%20debut%20at%20the%20Hangzhou%20showpiece%20where%20they%20made%20a%20group%20stage%20exit%20after%20losing%20both%20their%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENepal%20had%20amassed%20314%2F3%20against%20Mongolia%20on%20their%20international%20debut%2C%20a%20match%20they%20had%20lost%20by%20273%20runs%20after%20getting%20out%20for%2041.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMongolia%20had%20also%20lost%20to%20Maldives%20by%20nine%20wickets%20in%20the%20second%20match%20after%20posting%2060%20for%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20ICC%2C%20one%20Battulga%20Gombo%20was%20the%20'man%20behind%20cricket'%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%202014%20he%20convinced%20the%20municipal%20park%20authorities%20to%20grant%20rights%20to%20develop%20an%20area%20of%20wasteland%20into%20a%20cricket%20ground%2C%20and%20in%202015%2C%20with%20his%20friend%20Chris%20Hurd%2C%20he%20launched%20the%20Mongolian%20Cricket%20Seed%20Appeal%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20ICC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%20the%20schools'%20programme%20has%20grown%2C%20six%20provinces%20outside%20Ulaanbaatar%20are%20now%20playing%20the%20game%2C%20and%20indoor%20and%20outdoor%20tournaments%20are%20consistently%20being%20hel