e%20of%20the%20costliest%20apples%20worldwide.%20That%E2%80%99s%20how%20it%20gets%20its%20name%2C%20Black%20Gold.%20Its%20taste%2C%20crunchiness%2C%20and%20juiciness%20add%20to%20its%20uniqueness.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20it%20has%20a%20high%20value.%20And%20these%20can%20be%20grown%20only%20in%20our%20region%20given%20our%20climatic%20conditions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20Ashish%20aims%20to%20commercialise%20value-added%20products%20of%20these%20apples%20to%20further%20the%20income%20of%20regional%20farmers.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20aim%20to%20process%20apples%20into%20jams%2C%20vinegar%2C%20juices%2C%20and%20healthy%20dried%20apple%20chips.%20Our%20processing%20unit%20will%20be%20operational%20from%20September%20onwards%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reveals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%20at%20his%20city%20life%2C%20Ashish%20finds%20contentment%20in%20rural%20farm%20life.%20%E2%80%9CI%20enjoy%20my%20field%20of%20work%20as%20I%20get%20to%20meet%20real%20India%20%E2%80%93%20its%20small%20farmers.%20With%20my%20work%2C%20I%20see%20improvements%20in%20front%20of%20me%20every%20day.%20These%20farmers%20were%20once%20in%20distress%20and%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20middlemen.%20To%20be%20able%20to%20help%20them%20even%20on%20a%20very%20basic%20level%20is%20so%20fulfilling.%20We%20are%20not%20just%20helping%20a%20person%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20helping%20the%20whole%20family%20and%20the%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Ashish%20Negi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715177558000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FKinnaur-apples-2-1715174392.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D349336%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ashish%20Negi%20left%20his%20engineering%20career%20to%20revive%20ancestral%20apple%20orchards%20in%20Kinnaur.%20He%20now%20runs%20'Kayang'%20to%20empower%20local%20farmer