one%20buzzes.%20Anyone%20privy%20to%20the%20conversation%20would%20know%20that%20it%20is%20another%20patient%20on%20the%20line.%20She%20is%20running%20a%20fever%20and%20needs%20antibiotics%20urgently.%20Calling%20Dr%20Alam%20is%20one%20of%20her%20options%3B%20the%20other%20is%20a%20three-day%20walk%20from%20the%20remote%20island%20in%20the%20Sundarbans%20where%20she%20lives%20to%20the%20nearest%20Government%20hospital.%20It%20is%20a%20no-brainer%20which%20one%20she%20chooses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20hearing%20her%20out%20on%20the%20phone%2C%20Dr%20Alam%20shouts%20out%20instructions%20to%20someone%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20move%20fast.%E2%80%9D%20A%20few%20minutes%20later%2C%20the%20roaring%20of%20an%20engine%20is%20indicative%20of%20a%20boat%20preparing%20to%20head%20to%20its%20next%20destination.%20As%20the%20white%20vessel%20powers%20through%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F305137%2Fneelanjan-chakravarty-from-kolkata-builds-homestay-in-sunderbans-west-bengal-travel-vacation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewaters%20of%20the%20Sundarbans%3C%2Fa%3E%20(one%20of%20the%20largest%20mangrove%20forests%20in%20the%20world%20located%20in%20West%20Bengal)%2C%20the%20team%20inside%20%E2%80%94%20the%20doctor%2C%20a%20nurse%2C%20an%20x-ray%20technician%2C%20a%20lab%20technician%2C%20a%20pharmacist%20%E2%80%94%20busy%20themselves%20keeping%20medicines%20and%20equipment%20handy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20unique%20concept%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20month%2C%20we%20treat%2034%2C578%20patients%20in%20total%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Alam%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20shying%20away%20from%20taking%20credit%20for%20this%20massive%20volume.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20four%20boats%20in%20total%20and%20the%20schedule%20for%20each%20is%20set%20every%20Monday.%20Throughout%20the%20week%2C%20we%20travel%20across%20the%2030%20islands%20of%20the%20Sundarbans%2C%20covering%20six%20blocks%20in%20the%20North%20and%2013%20in%20the%20South.%20On%20Sundays%2C%20we%20return%20to%20the%20mainland%20where%20we%20stock%20up%20on%20supplies%2C%20medicines%2C%20rest%20and%20recharge%20for%20the%20next%20week.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Alam%20has%20been%20doing%20this%20for%20the%20last%2010%20years.%20In%20fact%2C%20he%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20doctors%20to%20be%20appointed%20by%20the%20couple%20Mohammed%20Abdul%20Wohab%20and%20Sabitri%20Pal%20%E2%80%94%20the%20founding%20members%20of%20the%20SHIS%20Foundation%20(Southern%20Health%20Improvement%20Samity)%20started%20in%201980%20%E2%80%94%20when%20Wohab%2C%20a%20lawyer%2C%20and%20Pal%2C%20a%20teacher%2C%20bonded%20over%20their%20intentions%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F278313%2Fsundarbans-hingalganj-island-english-medium-school-inspiring-teacher-kolkata%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echampion%20change%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20their%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98People%20were%20dying%20in%20front%20of%20my%20eyes%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E380%20mm%20of%20rainfall%20in%2024%20hours.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWest%20Bengal%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20able%20to%20forget%2027%20September%201978.%20Thousands%20died%2C%20starved%20and%20were%20left%20homeless%20as%20the%20torrential%20rain%20washed%20away%20entire%20houses.%20Wohab%2C%20who%20lived%20in%20Howrah%20at%20the%20time%2C%20recalls%20the%20harrowing%20ordeal.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20heartbreaking%20to%20watch%20people%20and%20their%20cattle%20drowning%20in%20the%20water.%20All%20around%2C%20flood%20victims%20were%20taking%20shelter%20in%20other%E2%80%99s%20homes%20and%20schools%2C%20and%20even%20climbing%20up%20trees%20to%20avoid%20drowning.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20knew%20what%20the%20next%20week%2C%20much%20less%20the%20next%20few%20days%2C%20would%20bring.%20