%2Fboeing-locks-out-firefighterse_n_66369468e4b00b1eab5377a5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20embattled%20aircraft%20manufacturer%20is%20at%20odds%20with%20the%20firefighters'%20union%20over%20a%20new%20contract.%20The%20union%20calls%20the%20lockout%20a%20safety%20risk.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A78%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fboeing-locks-out-firefighterse_n_66369468e4b00b1eab5377a5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-huffpost-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fboeing-locks-out-firefighterse_n_66369468e4b00b1eab5377a5%2Famp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fboeing-locks-out-firefighterse_n_66369468e4b00b1eab5377a5%2Famp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IFS%20Officer%20Transformed%20a%20Barren%20UP%20Land%20into%20His%20District%E2%80%99s%201st%20Eco-Tourism%20Hub%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20Indian%20Forest%20Service%20(IFS)%20officer%20Vikas%20Nayak%20saw%20the%20land%20where%20Rapdi%20Eco%20Tourism%20Centre%20stands%20today%2C%20he%20saw%20immense%20potential.%20Sitting%20barren%20right%20next%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F95718%2Fyamuna-river-pollution-scientists%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERiver%20Yamuna%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20place%20was%20a%20deserted%20land%20with%20dying%20biodiversity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20something%20about%20the%20land%20which%20made%20me%20want%20to%20conserve%20biodiversity.%20When%20I%20saw%20the%20place%2C%20I%20could%20envision%20a%20spot%20much%20more%20than%20a%20barren%20plot.%20I%20immediately%20started%20to%20draw%20a%20plan%20with%20my%20team%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConceptualised%20in%202023%2C%2011%20months%20later%2C%20Vikas%20was%20able%20to%20build%20Rapdi%20Ecotourism%20Centre%20along%20with%20his%20team.%20%E2%80%9COn%20its%20opening%20day%2C%20we%20had%20about%201%2C100%20people%20swarming%20the%20place%2C%20which%20is%20a%20lot%20for%20a%20place%20like%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20muses%20Vikas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20attempting%20to%20save%20the%20biodiversity%20of%20the%20place%20was%20a%20key%20factor%2C%20there%20was%20another%20reason%20to%20rejuvenate%20the%20place%20%E2%80%94%20spreading%20awareness%20about%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F282775%2Frobinson-crusoe-worlds-remotest-island-to-document-conserve-biodiversity%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econscious%20tourism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20ravine%20experience%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocated%20a%20short%20drive%20away%20from%20Shikohabad%20in%20the%20district%20of%20Firozabad%2C%20the%20place%20is%20home%20to%20hundreds%20of%20trees%2C%20wooden%20huts%2C%20boats%20and%20a%20lot%20more%20and%20was%20%E2%80%9Ctaken%20up%20to%20create%20the%20first%20ecotourism%20facility%20in%20the%20district.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20first%20posted%20in%20the%20area%2C%20I%20realised%20how%20it%20did%20not%20have%20any%20ecotourism%20place.%20The%20locals%20were%20not%20very%20active%20in%20natural%20conservation%20either%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20about%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20the%20officer%20started%20to%20look%20around%20the%20area%20and%20found%20the%20perfect%20place%20here%20itself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20perfect%20place%20as%20it%20had%20ravine%20qualities%20and%20also%20a%20little%20elevation.%20I%20got%20down%20to%20drawing%20plans%20and%20making%20a%20budget.%20We%20formulated%20a%20project%20and%20presented%20it%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%